Information: This file provides default values for the deployment wizard inside Visual Studio and the AWS Lambda commands added to the .NET Core CLI.

function-description: Core AI enrichment service for the tender pipeline. Consumes messages from the AI queue, calls AWS Bedrock to generate a summary, and sends the enriched tender to the tag queue for classification.
